{"type":"message","id":"05095a2d","parentId":"64a212d1","timestamp":"2026-04-14T00:33:05.283Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking why the prediction references April 11 data instead of April 13 data. They're right to question this - it's Tuesday April 14, so the most recent trading day should be April 13 (Monday), not April 11 (Friday).\n\nLet me check what data was actually available at the time of prediction. The prediction was generated at 2026-04-14T09:15:00+08:00. The market hasn't opened yet (opens at 9:30).\n\nThe issue is that April 13 (Monday) was a trading day, so there should be US market data for April 13. \n\nLooking at the data sources, the prediction is pulling Nasdaq and SOX closes from April 11 and 10, which means April 13 data wasn't available yet when the prediction was made - likely because US markets had already closed for the day and the data hadn't been updated in the system yet.","thinkingSignature":"1434023beb2166c290b5e874b1b7f16e6b36ea952cba18dcb42a31436c901569"},{"type":"text","text":"好问题，你说得对。\n\n目前系统里记录的最新美股数据是4/11（周五）的，**4/13（周一）的美股数据确实缺失**。\n\n原因可能是：\n- 预测生成时间（9:15）早于A股开盘\n- 数据源在那个时间点还没有抓取到4/13的美股收盘数据\n\n不过4/13（周一）美股实际上是**正常交易的**，所以最理想的情况应该参考4/13的数据而不是4/11。\n\n**换句话说：早盘预测中美股数据存在一天滞后，这是一个数据获取及时性的问题，不是框架问题。**\n\n要不要我立即去查一下4/13的最新纳指和费城半导体数据，然后看是否需要修正早盘预测？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":345,"cacheRead":22569,"cacheWrite":104,"totalTokens":23076,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.000414,"cacheRead":0.0013541399999999998,"cacheWrite":0.000039,"total":0.0018245399999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776126769837,"responseId":"062cbe313d1840d8d0b5a1047e013f3f"}}
