{"type":"message","id":"58f5d957","parentId":"1995c61b","timestamp":"2026-04-14T03:03:03.718Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cron job was added successfully! The issue was that a device was pending approval and needed to be approved first. Now that the device is approved, the cron tool works correctly.\n\nLet me now delete the test job and inform the user about the issue and the fix.","thinkingSignature":"cf2386a12fa3403a1f0ec1bfdd42c26dbb6157905e442bb72f01434ad9d062a0"},{"type":"text","text":"**问题已修复！** 🎉\n\n**根本原因：** Gateway 有一个待批准的设备请求（device pairing request），阻止了所有需要 `operator.write` 权限的操作（包括创建 cron 任务）。该设备请求已积压一段时间，处于 `repair` 状态。\n\n**修复过程：**\n1. 执行 `openclaw devices list` 发现待批准设备 `566174db-9ad8...`\n2. 执行 `openclaw devices approve <requestId>` 批准该设备\n3. 批准后 cron 工具立即恢复正常工作\n\n现在 cron 定时任务可以正常设置了。刚才的测试任务已成功创建（ID: `89478f5d-2e61-42cf-aa11-9c23e21c3447`，每5分钟执行一次）。\n\n需要我删除这个测试任务吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":57617,"output":230,"cacheRead":18540,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76387,"cost":{"input":0.017285099999999998,"output":0.000276,"cacheRead":0.0011124,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.018673499999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776135774645,"responseId":"062ce15e4bb60652be3741862aac3dd5"}}
