{"type":"message","id":"6beb5777","parentId":"ac5e9e12","timestamp":"2026-04-14T03:04:41.109Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to:\n1. Delete the test cron job that was just created\n2. Add a proper scheduled prediction task for 兆易创新\n\nLet me first delete the test job, then create a proper recurring cron job for the stock prediction.\n\nThe test job ID is: 89478f5d-2e61-42cf-aa11-9c23e21c3447\n\nFor the 兆易创新 prediction task, I should set up a daily cron job that runs before market opens (9:00 AM) and after market closes (15:00 PM or 15:30 PM). The user probably wants morning (AM) and possibly afternoon (PM) predictions.\n\nLooking at the task structure:\n\n\n- Morning prediction: before 9:30 AM (before market opens)\n- The user asked for \"早盘预测\" which means morning session prediction\n\nI should schedule:\n- Daily at 08:30 AM (Beijing time) for morning prediction - run in main session and deliver to feishu\n\nActually, let me think about this more carefully. The user wants scheduled predictions. Let me check the PROJECT_PLAN to understand the full workflow. The daily prediction workflow for 兆易创新 has morning and afternoon sessions, so I should probably set up both morning (08:30) and afternoon (14:30 or 15:00) cron jobs to deliver predictions before each market session.\n\nFor the cron job parameters, I need to use session:main to run in the main session, system-event as the payload kind to inject a reminder, and deliver the output directly to the user via feishu. I'll create two jobs: one at 08:30 Beijing time each weekday for the morning prediction, and another at 14:30 Beijing time for the afternoon prediction, both using cron expressions with the Asia/Shanghai timezone.\n\nNow I'll delete the test job and set up these two scheduled jobs.","thinkingSignature":"806662388043a513d2060844acf13757a12425799cf24cdd130d7c6137c9e64e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0vo62v568uo6_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"remove","jobId":"89478f5d-2e61-42cf-aa11-9c23e21c3447"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":452,"cacheRead":18540,"cacheWrite":52776,"totalTokens":71826,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.0005424,"cacheRead":0.0011124,"cacheWrite":0.019791,"total":0.021463199999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776135858381,"responseId":"062ce1b2c42d95fb8dcbd846666b701a"}}
