{"type":"message","id":"2166e466","parentId":"db88eaac","timestamp":"2026-04-14T03:05:03.765Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the test job is deleted. Now let me add the two prediction cron jobs for 兆易创新:1. Morning prediction at 08:30 Beijing time (weekdays only)2. Afternoon prediction at 14:30 Beijing time (weekdays only)\n\nActually, let me think about this. The market opens at 9:30 AM and closes at 15:00 PM (with after-hours until 15:30). The user asked for \"早盘预测\" which is morning session. They also had morning and afternoon session predictions in the PROJECT_PLAN.\n\nLet me set up:\n- Morning: 08:30 AM (before market opens) - deliver \"兆易创新早盘预测\" message\n\n\n- Afternoon: 14:30 PM (before afternoon session) - deliver \"兆易创新午盘/收盘预测\" message\n\nI'll use sessionTarget=\"isolated\" and let it announce results to feishu. The cron expression for weekdays at 08:30 would be \"30 8 * * 1-5\". For weekdays at 14:30, I'll use \"30 14 * * 1-5\". Both will use Asia/Shanghai timezone.\n\nFor the message, I'll craft something like \"兆易创新(603986)早盘预测任务\" to trigger the morning analysis, and I need to think through the payload structure for system-event versus agent-turn, considering how each delivers results.\n\nFor a reminder system, I should set sessionTarget=\"main\" with system-event kind so it sends a reminder to the main session. But the cron tool actually has a specific behavior where system-event payloads default to the main session, while agent-turn payloads default to isolated sessions. So I'll go with system-event for the reminder delivery.\n\nI can use the sessionTarget=\"current\" to have the cron run directly in the current chat thread, which would announce the result back to the same Feishu conversation. The cron expression would be \"30 8 * * 1-5\" with Asia/Shanghai timezone.\n\nActually, I think a cleaner approach is to have the cron job run in an isolated session where it performs the analysis, gets the results, and then announces the output back to the user on Feishu rather than trying to push it into the main session context.","thinkingSignature":"2e7adf9cbe0389995460513554b609dbcdd824f84a30b3d05404cd3a2db2359b"},{"type":"text","text":"测试任务已删除。现在添加兆易创新早晚盘定时预测任务：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8hdbqzae9a5a_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"兆易创新早盘预测","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"30 8 * * 1-5","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请执行兆易创新(603986)早盘预测任务：1) 读取 tracking/daily_prediction.json 了解当前状态；2) 获取最新股价数据；3) 生成早盘预测报告并更新 tracking/daily_prediction.json 的 am_session.prediction；4) 将完整预测结果回复给我。"}}}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8hdbqzae9a5a_2","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"兆易创新午盘/尾盘预测","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"30 14 * * 1-5","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请执行兆易创新(603986)午盘/尾盘预测任务：1) 读取 tracking/daily_prediction.json 了解早盘预测内容；2) 获取最新股价数据；3) 更新 tracking/daily_prediction.json 的 pm_session.prediction；4) 将完整午盘/尾盘预测结果回复给我。"}}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":53314,"output":813,"cacheRead":18540,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72667,"cost":{"input":0.0159942,"output":0.0009756,"cacheRead":0.0011124,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0180822}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776135881157,"responseId":"062ce1c9a968c47752aa4d82cc1f9d52"}}
