{"type":"message","id":"86940829","parentId":"4808d997","timestamp":"2026-04-14T03:07:04.701Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, now let me create the three cron jobs as specified in the project plan:\n1. 9:00 AM - 早盘预测 (AM prediction)\n2. 12:00 PM - 午盘复盘 + 下午预测 (Midday review + PM prediction)\n3. 15:00 PM - 尾盘复盘 (End of day review)\n\nI need to use cron expressions:\n- 9:00 on weekdays: \"0 9 * * 1-5\"\n- 12:00 on weekdays: \"0 12 * * 1-5\"\n- 15:00 on weekdays: \"0 15 * * 1-5\"\n\nLet me construct the messages properly based on the project plan.","thinkingSignature":"22bb9606ca0bfb30ff92257fe715611c603d0470949510c56298f89934cec4e1"},{"type":"text","text":"现在按方案设置三个定时任务：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7gg4rv4xx26s_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"兆易创新早盘预测","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 9 * * 1-5","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请执行兆易创新(603986)早盘预测任务：\n1) 读取 tracking/daily_prediction.json 了解当前状态；\n2) 通过腾讯财经API获取最新股价数据（开盘价、昨收价、成交量等）；\n3) 获取隔夜外围市场数据（纳指、费城半导体指数）；\n4) 按照15个维度(基本面/估值/行业面/资金面/技术面等)生成早盘预测报告；\n5) 更新 tracking/daily_prediction.json 的 am_session.prediction；\n6) 输出完整早盘预测报告（含方向/区间/概率分布/关键价位）。"}}}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7gg4rv4xx26s_2","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"兆易创新午盘复盘+下午预测","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 12 * * 1-5","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请执行兆易创新(603986)午盘复盘与下午预测任务：\n1) 读取 tracking/daily_prediction.json 的 am_session.prediction 内容；\n2) 通过腾讯财经API获取上午最新行情（开盘价、11:30收盘价、涨跌幅、成交量）；\n3) 对比早盘预测与实际走势，评估预测准确度；\n4) 生成午盘复盘报告（实际vs预测偏差分析）；\n5) 生成下午走势预测（含方向/区间/概率分布）；\n6) 更新 tracking/daily_prediction.json 的 am_session.review 和 pm_session.prediction。"}}}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7gg4rv4xx26s_3","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"兆易创新尾盘复盘","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 15 * * 1-5","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请执行兆易创新(603986)尾盘复盘任务：\n1) 读取 tracking/daily_prediction.json 的 pm_session.prediction 内容；\n2) 通过腾讯财经API获取下午最新行情（15:00收盘价、涨跌幅、全日成交量）；\n3) 对比下午预测与实际走势，评估预测准确度；\n4) 生成尾盘复盘报告（含全天走势总结、准确率统计、经验教训）；\n5) 更新 tracking/daily_prediction.json 的 pm_session.review；\n6) 更新 tracking/daily_price.json 全日行情数据；\n7) 统计并更新 overall accuracy_rate。"}}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":57013,"output":862,"cacheRead":18540,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76415,"cost":{"input":0.0171039,"output":0.0010344,"cacheRead":0.0011124,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0192507}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776136006845,"responseId":"062ce2468f0a50f086bb2e6d12d1153b"}}
