{"type":"message","id":"f7932837","parentId":"474c7483","timestamp":"2026-04-14T03:07:16.679Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All three cron jobs have been successfully created. Let me summarize the results for the user.","thinkingSignature":"1b1775655d49867345e97fb8d071a294ad7af73d41c39cc107600594e987e00c"},{"type":"text","text":"已按方案文档重新设置三个定时任务：\n\n| 任务 | Cron 表达式 | 执行时间 | 内容 |\n|------|-----------|---------|------|\n| 兆易创新早盘预测 | `0 9 * * 1-5` | **每天 09:00** | 15维度分析 → 输出预测报告 |\n| 兆易创新午盘复盘+下午预测 | `0 12 * * 1-5` | **每天 12:00** | 复盘上午 + 预测下午 |\n| 兆易创新尾盘复盘 | `0 15 * * 1-5` | **每天 15:00** | 全天复盘 + 准确率统计 |\n\n每个任务都会：\n- 读取 `tracking/daily_prediction.json` 当前状态\n- 通过腾讯财经API获取实时行情\n- 按方案中的15个维度进行分析\n- 更新对应 tracking 文件\n- 自动将报告推送至飞书"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":59101,"output":222,"cacheRead":18540,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77863,"cost":{"input":0.0177303,"output":0.00026639999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0011124,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0191091}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776136024832,"responseId":"062ce258b8720d0b75668c75f79e43f1"}}
