{"type":"message","id":"a2aaba9e","parentId":"7be65475","timestamp":"2026-04-14T03:10:10.591Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52ef4e292088c2e7dfbcd011bad\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_451d71ab5382024db03f3a5c37dcde02\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_451d71ab5382024db03f3a5c37dcde02\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-14 11:10 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_451d71ab5382024db03f3a5c37dcde02\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_451d71ab5382024db03f3a5c37dcde02\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_451d71ab5382024db03f3a5c37dcde02\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b52ef4e292088c2e7dfbcd011bad]\nou_451d71ab5382024db03f3a5c37dcde02: 两个方案同时使用"}],"timestamp":1776136210583}}
{"type":"message","id":"2464d62f","parentId":"a2aaba9e","timestamp":"2026-04-14T03:10:24.328Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to use both approaches - keep the cron running on weekdays and also add a reminder in heartbeat to check for holidays. Let me add a heartbeat reminder for the day before holidays, and also set up a reminder in the evening to check if the next day is a trading day.\n\nActually, looking at the heartbeat setup, I should set up a check for upcoming holidays. But since heartbeat runs every 30 minutes, it might be too frequent. Let me think about this...\n\nActually, a better approach would be to add a note to HEARTBEAT.md to check for upcoming holidays. But since HEARTBEAT.md is template-based and the user just wants to be reminded, I could also suggest a cron-based approach.\n\n\nA cron job that runs weekly before potential holiday periods could work well, or I could set up a daily reminder that triggers before major holidays. Let me propose setting up a lightweight heartbeat check for this.","thinkingSignature":"30d32427c03bbebabc41224189845c9ad3ce1843c83df75d26f26d971d00c419"},{"type":"text","text":"好主意，两个方案结合：\n\n1. **Cron 任务**（周一至周五自动执行）\n2. **HEARTBEAT 心跳提醒**（节假日前自动提醒手动暂停任务）\n\n我来更新 HEARTBEAT.md：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1paiy4wabmhy_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":275,"cacheRead":77810,"cacheWrite":1712,"totalTokens":79855,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.00033,"cacheRead":0.004668599999999999,"cacheWrite":0.000642,"total":0.005658}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776136210592,"responseId":"062ce31293771d38b6be3036676f352b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e11d6268","parentId":"2464d62f","timestamp":"2026-04-14T03:10:24.333Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1paiy4wabmhy_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md Template\n\n```markdown\n# Keep this file empty (or with only comments) to skip heartbeat API calls.\n\n# Add tasks below when you want the agent to check something periodically.\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776136224332}}
{"type":"message","id":"81e6c96c","parentId":"e11d6268","timestamp":"2026-04-14T03:10:39.903Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"HEARTBEAT.md is currently empty (just a template comment). I need to add a holiday check task. Since heartbeat runs every 30 minutes, I should make the task smart enough to only trigger alerts around holidays. Or I could add a note for myself to check holidays.\n\nActually, the best approach would be to add a daily check that runs once per day (e.g., on weekday mornings) to check if the next day is a holiday. But HEARTBEAT.md doesn't support time-based filtering easily.\n\nLet me think about this differently. I can add a task to the HEARTBEAT.md that checks for upcoming holidays and reminds to pause cron jobs. The heartbeat runs every 30 minutes, so I could write a note that the agent should check if tomorrow is a holiday and remind if so. \n\nI'll keep the logic simple—just a reminder to check if the next day is a holiday and pause cron jobs if needed.","thinkingSignature":"a1db9e93552759e3d2c8a4de6b7f0fd3a5da9c3ae0616889e24904c86eff308f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ozlvvtvwgkzk_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md","content":"# HEARTBEAT.md\n\n## 定期检查任务\n\n### 交易日历检查（周五检查）\n每个周五（如为工作日）检查下周的交易日历：\n- 如果下周一是法定节假日，提前提醒用户暂停兆易创新定时任务\n- 如果下周有调休工作日（周末变交易日），确认定时任务是否需调整\n\n### 检查提醒规则\n- 检查时间：每周五 09:00-10:00 之间\n- 如发现节假日/调休，回复提醒告知用户需手动暂停/恢复哪些定时任务\n- 不每日重复提醒，同一假期仅提醒一次\n\n## 兆易创新定时任务ID（供参考）\n| 任务 | Job ID | Cron |\n|------|--------|------|\n| 兆易创新早盘预测 | be7d5aa1-1a10-4cbc-ace4-059ea19b47ac | 周一至周五 09:00 |\n| 兆易创新午盘复盘+下午预测 | 6f06e0b0-aa42-4280-8d04-8dcbf5f2d053 | 周一至周五 12:00 |\n| 兆易创新尾盘复盘 | 90651347-0291-4e77-91df-f7d04350f196 | 周一至周五 15:00 |\n\n暂停任务命令：`openclaw cron update --jobId <id> --disabled`\n恢复任务命令：`openclaw cron update --jobId <id> --enabled`\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":61373,"output":556,"cacheRead":18540,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80469,"cost":{"input":0.0184119,"output":0.0006672,"cacheRead":0.0011124,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.020191499999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776136224337,"responseId":"062ce320638074085f2e8b6741627448"}}
