{"type":"message","id":"b4c45553","parentId":"f4bb64ea","timestamp":"2026-04-14T03:10:59.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I've updated the project plan with the dual approach. Now let me verify the changes are correct.","thinkingSignature":"b9839a048a21f64bcd828f8e25cc0ccee66533203d24999cbcd628046fbad331"},{"type":"text","text":"完成！现在的双重保障方案：\n\n**① Cron 定时任务**（周一至周五自动执行）\n| 时间 | 任务 |\n|------|------|\n| 09:00 | 早盘预测 |\n| 12:00 | 午盘复盘 + 下午预测 |\n| 15:00 | 尾盘复盘 |\n\n**② HEARTBEAT 心跳提醒**（每周五自动触发）\n- 检查下周是否涉及节假日/调休\n- 提前提醒用户手动暂停/恢复任务\n- 任务ID已记录在 `HEARTBEAT.md`\n\n这样即使 Cron 本身无法识别中国节假日，心跳会在每周五自动提醒，双重保障不遗漏。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":62762,"output":169,"cacheRead":18540,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81471,"cost":{"input":0.018828599999999997,"output":0.0002028,"cacheRead":0.0011124,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.020143799999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776136253742,"responseId":"062ce33deae2c5a944a721055d415ed2"}}
