{"type":"message","id":"37a3d9be","parentId":"1d5bebbb","timestamp":"2026-04-14T03:12:22.884Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to integrate a China trading calendar API to automatically handle holidays. This would allow the cron jobs to automatically skip holidays. Let me think about how to implement this.\n\nOptions for China trading calendar APIs:\n1. akshare - Python library with China stock calendar data\n2. tushare - China stock data API\n3. baostock - China stock data\n4. Some free HTTP APIs\n\nThe most practical approach would be:\n1. Create a script or skill that checks if today is a trading day\n2. Use this in the cron job workflow - but cron jobs are scheduled, not conditional\n\nActually, the cron jobs are cron expressions - they run on a schedule regardless. We can't conditionally skip them via cron itself. \n\nThe best approach is:\n1. Create a script that checks China trading calendar (using akshare or similar)\n2. At the start of each cron job, the agent checks if today is a trading day\n3. If not a trading day, skip the prediction and exit early\n\nOr alternatively:\n- Create a daily trigger at 8:30 AM that checks if today is a trading day, and if so, enables the cron jobs for that day, otherwise disables them\n\nActually, the cleanest approach for a Linux/server setup would be:\n1. Install `akshare` or `pandas_trading_calendars` (but pandas_trading_calendars primarily for US markets)\n2. Use `akshare` to get China stock exchange calendar\n\n\n3. Embed this check directly in the agent's prompt at the start of each prediction task - if today isn't a trading day, it exits without generating predictions\n\nI could use a public HTTP API like Sina or Tencent Finance to check if today is a trading day, which would be simpler than installing a library. The key is that the cron job triggers the agent, then the agent itself checks the calendar before doing any work.","thinkingSignature":"7f3559b373fbce78732303068e03f2807629cb5eaaf1927f757a72c06ec1e89b"},{"type":"text","text":"可以！我来设置一个中国交易日历 API 自动检查机制。\n\n方案：在每个预测任务执行时，agent 会先检查今天是否为交易日，非交易日则直接跳过。\n\n先测试几个可用的中国交易日历接口：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_71mrdm0azdd5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"http://tool.sLeon.com.cn/api/v1/trade-calendar?date=$(date +%Y%m%d)\" 2>/dev/null | head -3 || curl -s \"https://api.s Leon.com.cn/trade-calendar?date=$(date +%Y%m%d)\" 2>/dev/null | head -3"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_71mrdm0azdd5_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://www.akdataapi.com/api/tradedate?date=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\" 2>/dev/null | head -3 || curl -s \"https://api.tushare.pro/?api_name=trade_cal&params='{\"exchange\":\"SSE\",\"start_date\":\"$(date +%Y%m%d)\",\"end_date\":\"$(date +%Y%m%d)\"}'\" 2>/dev/null | head -3"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":650,"cacheRead":79758,"cacheWrite":1438,"totalTokens":81904,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.00078,"cacheRead":0.00478548,"cacheWrite":0.00053925,"total":0.00612213}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776136318422,"responseId":"062ce37e17ef305ba9c37f833fc9189e"}}
