{"type":"message","id":"59df8d43","parentId":"f0064ba7","timestamp":"2026-04-14T03:13:38.146Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Tencent Finance API works. Now let me think of a way to check if today is a trading day. \n\nActually, the simplest approach that would work reliably:\n1. Write a shell script that uses `date` command to check if today is Saturday or Sunday\n2. For holidays, we could maintain a simple list in a file, or rely on the heartbeat mechanism\n\nLet me create a script at `/root/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/is_trading_day.sh` that:\n- Checks if today is weekend (Sat/Sun) → return 1 (not trading day)\n- Checks against a simple holiday list → return 1 if holiday\n- Otherwise → return 0 (trading day)\n\nFor the holiday list, I could:\n1. Hardcode known 2026 holidays\n2. Or fetch from a web API\n\nActually, a simpler approach: the agent can do a web search at the start of each task to check if today is a trading day. This is dynamic and doesn't require maintaining a holiday list.\n\nBut wait - the user asked for API integration. Let me try one more approach. \n\nActually let me check if there's a simpler way. The Sina Finance API or similar might have a way to get the trading calendar.\n\nLet me try another approach: Use `jq` or Python to parse the Tencent API response and see if we can get some market open/close status.\n\nActually, the simplest solution for now would be to:\n1. Create a shell script `/root/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/is_trading_day.sh` that:\n   - Checks if today is weekend (easy via `date +%w`)\n   - Has a simple holiday list hardcoded\n   - Makes a quick HTTP check to a known endpoint that tells us if the market is open\n\n2. Update the HEARTBEAT.md to remind about holidays on Fridays\n\n3. The cron job prompts can also be updated to instruct the agent to check if today is a trading day at the start\n   \nI think I should go ahead and build this script now.","thinkingSignature":"7ed4fc548cf2efefa22afc89e9b6ca4ced8b51aae031bf36057d91219c012f8b"},{"type":"text","text":"腾讯财经API可用。我来创建一个中国交易日历检查脚本，结合API + 节假日列表：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_av0kbbzpiumo_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /root/.openclaw/workspace/scripts && ls /root/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":65304,"output":483,"cacheRead":18540,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84327,"cost":{"input":0.0195912,"output":0.0005796,"cacheRead":0.0011124,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0212832}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776136403402,"responseId":"062ce3d399c14b84a0dfe02f804a6f98"}}
