{"type":"message","id":"8764e8d8","parentId":"fd564c93","timestamp":"2026-04-14T03:14:14.673Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The script works. Today is a trading day (Tuesday, April 14, 2026). Now let me also update the HEARTBEAT.md to note the script location, and update the cron job prompts to use this script to skip non-trading days.But wait - the cron jobs themselves are cron expressions that run regardless of whether it's a trading day. The script needs to be called by the agent (via exec tool) at the start of each task to check if it's a trading day and skip if not.Let me update the HEARTBEAT.md to include the script reference, and update the cron job prompts to include a check at the start.Actually, let me update the HEARTBEAT.md to document this:","thinkingSignature":"c321b91b5ae224af55d42ad100cd985fe87fdf9114401758a09ec624a4bdbf7c"},{"type":"text","text":"脚本工作正常！今天是交易日（周二）。现在更新 HEARTBEAT.md 记录脚本位置，并更新 cron 任务提示词加入交易日检查：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_oxn15trwxgyl_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md","content":"# HEARTBEAT.md\n\n## 定期检查任务\n\n### 交易日历检查（周五检查）\n每个周五（如为工作日）检查下周的交易日历：\n- 如果下周一是法定节假日，提前提醒用户暂停兆易创新定时任务\n- 如果下周有调休工作日（周末变交易日），确认定时任务是否需调整\n\n### 检查提醒规则\n- 检查时间：每周五 09:00-10:00 之间\n- 如发现节假日/调休，回复提醒告知用户需手动暂停/恢复哪些定时任务\n- 不每日重复提醒，同一假期仅提醒一次\n\n## 兆易创新定时任务ID（供参考）\n| 任务 | Job ID | Cron |\n|------|--------|------|\n| 兆易创新早盘预测 | be7d5aa1-1a10-4cbc-ace4-059ea19b47ac | 周一至周五 09:00 |\n| 兆易创新午盘复盘+下午预测 | 6f06e0b0-aa42-4280-8d04-8dcbf5f2d053 | 周一至周五 12:00 |\n| 兆易创新尾盘复盘 | 90651347-0291-4e77-91df-f7d04350f196 | 周一至周五 15:00 |\n\n暂停任务命令：`openclaw cron update --jobId <id> --disabled`\n恢复任务命令：`openclaw cron update --jobId <id> --enabled`\n\n## 中国交易日历脚本\n- 路径：`~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/is_trading_day.sh`\n- 用法：`bash is_trading_day.sh`\n- 返回 0：是交易日；返回 1：非交易日\n- 逻辑：周末判断 + 2026年法定节假日列表 + 腾讯财经API双重验证\n- **非交易日时，agent应直接输出\"今日非A股交易日，跳过预测\"并结束任务**\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":66905,"output":638,"cacheRead":18540,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86083,"cost":{"input":0.0200715,"output":0.0007656,"cacheRead":0.0011124,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.021949499999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776136440329,"responseId":"062ce3f8cc03faa3343aa1b27ad82f02"}}
