{"type":"message","id":"dd3aaa85","parentId":"6ef4d7ce","timestamp":"2026-04-14T03:14:21.593Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to update the cron job prompts to instruct the agent to check the trading calendar at the start. Let me update each cron job's message to include the trading day check.","thinkingSignature":"333705ad016a008db84b88621e131492b1239a6bff0149f5422f73f382e5b4cc"},{"type":"text","text":"现在更新三个 cron 任务的提示词，在执行前先检查是否为交易日：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_w8kq864wbki5_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"be7d5aa1-1a10-4cbc-ace4-059ea19b47ac","patch":{"payload":{"message":"请执行兆易创新(603986)早盘预测任务：\n1) 首先执行 `bash ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/is_trading_day.sh` 检查今日是否为交易日，如非交易日则回复\"今日非A股交易日，跳过早盘预测\"并结束任务；\n2) 读取 tracking/daily_prediction.json 了解当前状态；\n3) 通过腾讯财经API获取最新股价数据（开盘价、昨收价、成交量等）；\n4) 获取隔夜外围市场数据（纳指、费城半导体指数）；\n5) 按照15个维度(基本面/估值/行业面/资金面/技术面等)生成早盘预测报告；\n6) 更新 tracking/daily_prediction.json 的 am_session.prediction；\n7) 输出完整早盘预测报告（含方向/区间/概率分布/关键价位）。"}}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":67578,"output":311,"cacheRead":18540,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86429,"cost":{"input":0.0202734,"output":0.00037319999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0011124,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.021759}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776136454692,"responseId":"062ce406574c5e23d0d7538dc25fbf1f"}}
