{"type":"message","id":"12ceff42","parentId":"8c8e4ecb","timestamp":"2026-04-14T04:24:46.524Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if I have a K-line (candlestick chart) analysis skill. Let me check the available skills. I recall there's a `trading-knowledge` skill that covers K-line patterns, support/resistance, etc. and also a `china-stock-analysis` skill.","thinkingSignature":"7072d13611368a0c2c8d815a2dc51bbd8bb95becd9d5404bb458c5c24c7a3f85"},{"type":"text","text":"有的！我有相关技能可以用：\n\n**已有相关技能：**\n\n| 技能 | 功能 | 触发关键词 |\n|------|------|-----------|\n| `trading-knowledge` | K线形态、均线系统、MACD/RSI/KDJ、支撑阻力位、筹码分布、量价关系等技术分析 | 技术分析、K线、MACD、均线 |\n| `china-stock-analysis` | A股基本面+技术面综合分析、买卖建议 | 股票分析、A股 |\n\n如果需要更专业的K线分析，可以结合使用：\n- 腾讯财经API获取K线数据 → trading-knowledge 框架分析\n- 兆易创新今日K线数据 → 我可以实时拉取并画ASCII图\n\n需要我现在拉一下兆易创新的今日分时数据或K线数据来做分析吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":226,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":86843,"totalTokens":87127,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.0002712,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.032566125,"total":0.032854725}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776140677043,"responseId":"062cf485223dd0f72c32187cb6f8c4fa"}}
